<title>ạ̉nạ mryḍẗ ḥbạaⁿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - ạ̉nạ mryḍẗ ḥbaⁿạ bḥbyby

[V2]
 hyạ ạsndwny bạ̉qrạṣi ạlzbybi

[V3]
 wạnʿsẖwny bạltfạḥi

[V4]
 1- (līuqabĩl̊niy biqub̊lạati famihi fḥubãka ạảṭ̊yabu mina ạl̊kẖam̊ri)2

[V5]
 ạuj̊dẖub̊nī warāʾaka fanaj̊rīa ại̹lay̱ ḥijālik rby ạdkẖlny

[V6]
 2- (fạlsẖãm̊su qad̊ lawãḥat̊niy gẖaḍibūạ ʿalayã banū ạủmĩy)2

[V7]
 ạảkẖ̊bir̊nī yā man̊ tuḥibũhu naf̊sī ạảẙna tar̊ʿay̱ ạảẙna tur̊biḍ̊

[V8]
 3- (kāltũfãạḥi kdẖạ ḥabībiy taḥ̊ta ẓilĩhi ạ̉nạ jlstu)2

[V9]
 watẖamaratuhu ḥul̊waẗ liḥal̊qī baẙna ạl̊banīna lạ mtẖla lhu

[V10]
 4- (sẖimāluhu taḥ̊ta rā̊̉sī wayamīnuhu tuʿāniqunī)2

[V11]
 ạảd̊kẖalanī ại̹lay̱ baẙti ạl̊kẖam̊ri waʿalamuhu faẘqiy maḥabãẗ</lyrics>
</song>